[gd_scene load_steps=22 format=3 uid="uid://locale_hce_terrain_v1"]

; ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
; VOL 6 · HCE TERRAIN-ONLY · just the land
;
; Loads harmony_terrain.glb (built by build_harmony_terrain.py)
; — heightmap + creek water surface. Per the locale design
; manual (lore/_LOCALE_DESIGN_MANUAL.md): verify the terrain
; first, before laying roads or foundations.
;
; Player spawns up on the country-club hilltop so the first view
; reveals the whole district's topography sloping down to the
; creek and SE low ground. F11 cycles time-of-day so you can
; read the grades from different sun angles.
; ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

