; Player spawns on the country-club hilltop. HCE world (0, +380)
; sits at the cc_rise peak (~22 m + tilt + noise ≈ 27 m elevation).
; gltf swap (x_b, y_b, z_b) → (x_b, z_b, -y_b) → Godot (0, 30, -380).
; The 30 m camera height clears any noise wobble; player falls
; onto the hilltop on first frame and sees the whole district
; sloping down to the south. Far plane 1500 m so the SE basin
; stays visible.
[node name="Player" type="CharacterBody3D" parent="."]
transform = Transform3D(1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 30, -380)
script = ExtResource("2_fpc")
groups = ["player"]

[node name="CollisionShape3D" type="CollisionShape3D" parent="Player"]
shape = SubResource("Caps_Player")
transform = Transform3D(1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0.85, 0)

